title: We're Wired With God's Power | Victoria Osteen
itunes:title: We're Wired With God's Power | Victoria Osteen
description:
When you make Jesus the Lord of your life, you become fully connected to your source of power. All you have to do is switch it on!

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
